loyalty, commitment, courage, bravery, unity and discipline
during the war of liberation, can provide the hard core of the
party which can help withstand the influence of "the unseasoned
and inconstant elements always ready to go with the wind, the
opportunists".
</P>
<P>
"The party and government have decided to define and set up a
package for each war veteran along the lines traditionally,"
Mugabe said.
</P>
<P>
The package will enable the veterans to enjoy benefits such as
free education, priority in allocation of accommodation and free
health services.
</P>
