<HEADLINE> Historic Importance of Party Congress (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Workers at the Baotou Steel Complex, in the Inner Mongolia
Autonomous Region, held panel discussions on upholding the great
banner of Deng Xiaoping Theory, according to Plant Director Qin
Yichuan. "We believe the company will develop further as the
result of enterprise reform carried out under the guidance of Deng
Xiaoping Theory," said Qin.
</P>
<P>
On Friday, 100 military officers from the Nanjing Military Area
Command of the People's Liberation Army (PLA) gathered in a small
building at the Nanchang Army Institute, where Deng Xiaoping lived
between October 1969 and February 1973.
</P>
<P>
The officers studied Jiang's report to the congress and shared
the view that experience proves that upholding the great banner of
Deng Xiaoping Theory is the only way to ensure a good future for
the Party, the hopes of socialism and China's prosperity in the
21st century.
</P>
<P>
The decision of the congress to hold high the great banner of
Deng Xiaoping Theory has attracted strong response from the
nation's political and social science researchers.
</P>
<P>
Zhang Binshen, deputy-director of the Economics Institute at
the Jinan University in Guangzhou, capital of Guangdong Province,
said that Deng Xiaoping's Theory for guiding the country to
prosperity reflects the practical situation in China, as well as
the worldwide economic trend.
</P>
<P>
Professor Wang Lanyuan, deputy-director of the Marism-Leninism
Research Institute at Tianjin Normal University, said: "The issue
of banner is a crucial one, as proven by the history of socialist
movements in China and throughout the world."
</P>
