<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 20 (Xinhua) -- The General Office of the
Communist Party of China (CPC) Central Committee today issued a
circular calling for CPC committees at all levels to organize
Party members to study documents of the Party's 15th National
Congress.
</P>
