<HEADLINE> G7 Ministers Meet Prior to WB/IMF Annual Meetings </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, September 20 (Xinhua) -- The finance ministers and
governors of central banks of the Group of Seven (G-7)
industrialized countries today discussed key issues of global
economic development prior to the World Bank/International
Monetary Fund annual meetings to be held here next week.
</P>
<P>
