<P>
WASHINGTON -- The United States said Friday that it did not
offer new aid food to the Democratic People's Republic of Korea
(DPRK) in connection with four-party peace talks in New York.
</P>
<P>
"We have not and will not link North Korea's participation in
the four-party talks to other issues including food and therefore
