<DOCNO> XIE19970920.0210 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-09-20 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Costa Rica Denies Mass Deportation of Nicaraguans </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SAN JOSE, September 19 (Xinhua) -- Costa Rica today rejected an
allegation that it has deported large numbers of Nicaraguans.
</P>
<P>
Nicaragua claimed last week that 1,024 Nicaraguans were
deported from Costa Rica.
</P>
<P>
Costa Rican Immigration Director Mercedes Bevacqua said that
Nicaragua's figure does not agree with reality. She said that only
30 to 40 Nicaraguans are deported in a normal day and 60 on
weekends.
</P>
<P>
She said that the 1,024 cases mentioned by the Nicaraguan
authorities include persons rejected at the border when they
intended to enter the country.
</P>
<P>
The Costa Rican authorities say that more than 300,000
Nicaraguans are residing, most of them illegally, in this
country. They account for nearly 10 percent of the total
population.
</P>
<P>
The Nicaraguans in Costa Rica normally work in the agricultural
sector, especially in the northern regions. Some of them, however,
work as domestic assistants in the urban areas. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> XIE19970920.0211 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-09-20 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Jiangxi Province Aims for Sustained Growth </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 20 (Xinhua) -- Meilin Model Base of
Ecological Agriculture is located in south Jiangxi, a mountainous
area which was dubbed "desert in the south."
</P>
<P>
The base, however, has turned into a place of "green mountain
and clear water" after years of work with the province's Mountain,
River and Lake Project since the middle 1980s, according to
today's "China Daily".
</P>
<P>
A comprehensive development model is applied to develop, as a
whole, the agriculture, husbandry, fishery and commerce of an area
to fight soil erosion.
</P>
<P>
On the top of the mountain, trees and grasses are planted; at
the middle of the mountain, fruit trees are grown; at the foot of
the mountain, animals and poultry are raised; and in the valley,
water is dammed for fish, forming a multi-layered, integrated
agricultural system.
</P>
<P>
At the same time, products from the base are sold, earning
money for the farmers.
</P>
<P>
In 1994, the total production of the base more than quadrupled
that before the Mountain, River, Lake Project was
launched. Thirty-six hectares of the 39 hectares bare mountain
have been forested to completely control soil erosion,
strengthening the ecology.
</P>
<P>
When President Jiang Zemin visited the base in September 1996,
he praised the combination of poverty-relief with comprehensive
development for improving the environment.
</P>
<P>
At least 112 large bases for comprehensive development such as
Meilin have been successfully established in line with the
Mountain, River and Lake Project in Jiangxi Province. There are
also 26 experimental model bases to address nine problems,
including comprehensive development in the mountain and lake
areas, reformation of the Red Soil hilly land, and desert land.
</P>
<P>
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
